profile.MEDIUM=§aMedium
profile.HIGH=§6§lHigh
profile.EXTREME=§c§lExtreme §4§o(No Limits)

profile.comment=§aMedium§r: Smooth and friendly. §6§lHigh§r: Premium quality with SSR, dynamic clouds, AO and volumetric light. §c§lExtreme§r: EVERYTHING maxed — 64-step SSR, DOF, POM, Motion Blur, FXAA, max AO, dense clouds, realistic puddles. Requires a powerful GPU.

